<p class="ql-align-center">注意啦！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自7月起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>雨湖公安加大</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>打击非法捕捞犯罪专项行动力度的同时</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">各派出所对全区重点水域禁渔工作</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">展开多种形式的宣传和巡查</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200914/7723bb3ae35241ba811561940270459f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
